# AI Smart Attendance System

An intelligent attendance tracking system using facial recognition and computer vision to automate attendance management.

## Features

- 👤 **Facial Recognition**: Identify students using AI-powered face detection
- 📊 **Real-time Tracking**: Live attendance monitoring and reporting
- 📈 **Analytics Dashboard**: Visualize attendance patterns and statistics
- 🔐 **Secure**: User authentication and role-based access control
- 📱 **Responsive UI**: Mobile-friendly web interface
- 🗄️ **Database Integration**: Persistent storage of attendance records

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Python 3.9+**
- **Flask** - Web framework
- **OpenCV** - Computer vision library
- **face-recognition** - Facial recognition
- **SQLAlchemy** - ORM
- **PostgreSQL** - Database

### Frontend
- **React 18** - UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **Tailwind CSS** - Styling
- **Axios** - HTTP client
- **Chart.js** - Data visualization

